                                </bibl>), mens <name type="person" key="OleWid001">Ole
                                    Widding</name> og <name type="person" key="SteKar001">Stefán
                                    Karlsson</name> senere har dateret det mere præcist til
                                    <origDate notBefore="1300" notAfter="1325" evidence="conjecture" resp="ONP">1300-tallets første fjerdedel.</origDate>
                                    (<bibl>Widding: <ref type="secondary" target="HandskrWidding1960">
                                        Håndskriftsanalyser</ref>
                           <biblScope type="pages">91</biblScope>
                        </bibl> og <bibl>Karlsson: <ref type="secondary" target="EIMF7">Sagas of Icelandic
                                        Bishops</ref>
                           <biblScope type="volume">VII</biblScope>
                           <biblScope type="pages">59</biblScope>
                        </bibl>).</p>
                            <p>Ifølge Ole Widding har AM 325 VIII 3 c 4to <ref type="ms" target="#AM04-0325-VIII-4-a-da">AM 325 VIII 4 a 4to</ref>
                                sandsynligvis oprindelig tilhørt samme codex.</p>
                        </origin>
                        <provenance>
